From the inception of Dr. Tedros' bid for the position of Director General he has  been followed with international endorsements, shows of support, and backing. Influential individuals and organisations from across the globe have vouched for Dr. Tedros Adhanom, showing their support for him in words, testimonies, articles, videos, and more. Together with Dr. Tedros, the groups and individuals found below have shared a vision for a better WHO and have placed their full confidence in Dr. Tedros Adhanom.


